'''威廉·傑克森·哈珀'''（{{lang|en|William Jackson Harper}}，本名'''威廉·菲茨杰拉德·哈珀'''（{{lang|en|William Fitzgerald Harper}}），{{bd|1980年|2月8日}}）是一位美國演員，曾在美國[[國家廣播公司|國家廣播公司]]（NBC）2016年至2020年播出的情境電視喜劇《[[良善之地|良善之地]]》中，飾演主要角色「其迪·安那哥尼亞」（{{lang|fr|Chidi Anagonye}}）。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Saclao|first1=Christian|title='The Good Place' Actor William Jackson Harper on Playing Kristen Bell's Onscreen Soulmate in the NBC Series|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/good-place-actor-william-jackson-harper-playing-kristen-bells-onscreen-soulmate-nbc-2421790|work=[[國際財經時報|International Business Times]]|accessdate=2017-01-06|date=2016-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170107004604/http://www.ibtimes.com/good-place-actor-william-jackson-harper-playing-kristen-bells-onscreen-soulmate-nbc-2421790|archive-date=2017-01-07|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Charles|first1=Marissa|title=William Jackson Harper on Starring in NBC's 'The Good Place'|url=http://www.ebony.com/entertainment-culture/the-good-place-william-jackson-harper|work={{link-en|鳥木|Ebony (magazine)|Ebony}}|accessdate=2017-01-06|date=2016-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170107004824/http://www.ebony.com/entertainment-culture/the-good-place-william-jackson-harper|archive-date=2017-01-07|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 早年生活 ==
威廉·傑克森·哈珀是藝名，他本名威廉·菲茨杰拉德·哈珀（{{lang|en|William Fitzgerald Harper}}）<ref name=vulture>{{Cite news|url=https://www.vulture.com/2017/11/william-jackson-harper-on-the-good-place.html?sf134198415=1|title=William Jackson Harper on the Other Good Place Character He'd Like to Play|last=Pape|first=Allie|work=Vulture|access-date=2017-11-01|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107032053/http://www.vulture.com/2017/11/william-jackson-harper-on-the-good-place.html?sf134198415=1|archive-date=2017-11-07|dead-url=no}}</ref> 生於1980年2月8日的美國[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]][[達拉斯|達拉斯]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.playbill.com/person/william-jackson-harper-vault-0000125026|title=William Jackson Harper|work={{link-en|節目單|Playbill|Playbill}}|language=en|access-date=2017-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170731185352/http://www.playbill.com/person/william-jackson-harper-vault-0000125026|archive-date=2017-07-31|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2003年，哈珀自{{link-en|聖塔菲藝術與設計大學|Santa Fe University of Art and Design|聖塔菲學院}}畢業。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://santafeuniversity.edu/academics/performing-arts/performing-arts-accomplishments/alumni/|title=Alumni|publisher={{link-en|聖塔菲藝術與設計大學|Santa Fe University of Art and Design|Santa Fe University of Art and Design}}|language=en|access-date=2017-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171004085118/http://santafeuniversity.edu/academics/performing-arts/performing-arts-accomplishments/alumni/|archive-date=2017-10-04|dead-url=no}}</ref> 申請加入{{link-en|演員權益協會|Actors' Equity Association}}時，他選擇「威廉·傑克森·哈珀」（{{lang|en|William Jackson Harper}}）作為藝名；「威廉·哈珀」（{{lang|en|William Harper}}）的名字已被登記使用，「菲茨杰拉德」（{{lang|en|Fitzgerald}}）這個[[中間名|中間名]]又太長，於是他以母親的中間名「傑克森」（{{lang|en|Jackson}}），當作藝名的中間名，以紀念母親。<ref name=vulture/>

== 職業生涯 ==
哈珀在2014年首次登台，於[[百老匯|百老匯]]舞台劇《{{link-en|一路到底|All the Way (play)}}》中飾演詹姆斯·哈里遜（{{lang|en|James Harrison}}）與{{link-en|斯托克利·卡邁克爾|Stokely Carmichael}}。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.playbill.com/playbillpagegallery/inside-playbill?asset=00000150-ac87-d16d-a550-ecbf7e6b0005&type=InsidePlaybill&slide=1|title=Inside Playbill Gallery|work=Playbill|access-date=2017-10-03|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171003075626/http://www.playbill.com/playbillpagegallery/inside-playbill?asset=00000150-ac87-d16d-a550-ecbf7e6b0005&type=InsidePlaybill&slide=1|archive-date=2017-10-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2009年至2011年間，哈珀曾出演{{link-en|公共廣播電視公司兒童台|PBS Kids}}（PBS）的兒童電視連續劇《{{link-en|電力公司 (2009年電視連續劇)|The Electric Company (2009 TV series)|電力公司}}》。<ref name=":0" />

2016年，哈珀出演國家廣播公司（NBC）喜劇《良善之地》。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://deadline.com/2016/02/good-place-william-jackson-harper-cast-nbc-series-1201701275/|title='Good Place' NBC Comedy Series Casts William Jackson Harper|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=2016-02-12|work=Deadline|access-date=2018-01-30|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180527152356/http://deadline.com/2016/02/good-place-william-jackson-harper-cast-nbc-series-1201701275/|archive-date=2018-05-27|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在確定飾演主要角色其迪·安那哥尼亞（{{lang|fr|Chidi Anagonye}}）之前，他曾考慮要離開演藝生涯。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://ew.com/tv/2017/07/12/good-place-season-2-william-jackson-harper-chidi/|title='The Good Place' Star William Jackson Harper Promises 'Acupuncture and Pigs' in Season 2|last=Snierson|first=Dan|date=2017-07-12|work=[[娛樂週刊|Entertainment Weekly]]|access-date=2017-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171003075305/http://ew.com/tv/2017/07/12/good-place-season-2-william-jackson-harper-chidi/|archive-date=2017-10-03|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.eurweb.com/2016/09/good-place-saved-william-jackson-harper-quitting-hollywood-eur-exclusive/|title='The Good Place' Saved William Jackson Harper From Quitting Hollywood|last=Magee|first=Ny|date=2016-09-25|work=EURweb|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180130042603/https://www.eurweb.com/2016/09/good-place-saved-william-jackson-harper-quitting-hollywood-eur-exclusive/|archive-date=2018-01-30|language=en|accessdate=2020-08-06|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在他還未正式進入劇組前，劇組都沒有向他告知劇情大綱。<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://www.gq.com/story/william-jackson-harper-the-good-place-interview|title=The Good Place's William Jackson Harper Had No Idea What He Was Auditioning For|last=Meslow|first=Scott|date=2018-01-04|work=[[GQ|GQ]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180130040234/https://www.gq.com/story/william-jackson-harper-the-good-place-interview|archive-date=2018-01-30|language=en|accessdate=2020-08-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://collider.com/the-good-place-season-2-william-jackson-harper-interview/|title='The Good Place': William Jackson Harper on That Big Twist and Season 2 Challenges|last=Radish|first=Christina|date=2017-10-05|work=[[Collider_(website)|Collider]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180130043842/http://collider.com/the-good-place-season-2-william-jackson-harper-interview/|archive-date=2018-01-30|language=en|accessdate=2020-08-06|dead-url=no}}</ref> 而他在《良善之地》裡的演技則受到好評。<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://tv.avclub.com/the-good-place-ends-an-outstanding-first-season-with-it-1798190195|title=The Good Place ends an outstanding first season with its most masterful twist yet|last=Perkins|first=Dennis|date=19 January 2017|work=[[The_A.V._Club|The A.V. Club]]|access-date=2018-01-30|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180130204416/https://tv.avclub.com/the-good-place-ends-an-outstanding-first-season-with-it-1798190195|archive-date=2018-01-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://blog.apaonline.org/2017/06/21/philosophy-on-tv-the-good-place/|title=Philosophy on TV: "The Good Place"|last=Cleary|first=Skye|date=2017-06-21|publisher=[[美國哲學學會|American Philosophical Association]]|access-date=2018-01-30|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180131014551/https://blog.apaonline.org/2017/06/21/philosophy-on-tv-the-good-place/|archive-date=2018-01-31|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2017年，在拍攝《良善之地》第一季與第二季之間，他參與演出劇作家[[柔依·卡山|柔依·卡山]]在[[林肯表演藝術中心|林肯表演藝術中心]]克萊爾·陶劇院（{{lang|en|Claire Tow Theatre}}）公演的作品《狂歡之後》（{{lang|en|After the Blast}}）。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.lct.org/shows/after-blast/|title=After The Blast|publisher=[[林肯表演藝術中心|Lincoln Center Theater]]|language=en|access-date=2018-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180220152000/http://www.lct.org/shows/after-blast/|archive-date=2018-02-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/10/23/theater/review-romancing-the-bot-in-zoe-kazans-after-the-blast.html|title=Review: Romancing the Bot in Zoe Kazan's 'After the Blast'|last=Brantley|first=Ben|date=2017-10-23|work=[[紐約時報|The New York Times]]|access-date=2018-02-19|language=en|issn=0362-4331|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180220151859/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/10/23/theater/review-romancing-the-bot-in-zoe-kazans-after-the-blast.html|archive-date=2018-02-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年，哈珀出演兩部備受讚譽的電影：[[艾瑞·艾斯特|艾瑞·艾斯特]]編導的《[[仲夏魘|仲夏魘]]》與[[陶德·海恩斯|陶德·海恩斯]]執導的《[[黑水風暴|黑水風暴]]》。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://variety.com/2019/film/reviews/midsommar-film-review-1203247188/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190619231443/https://variety.com/2019/film/reviews/midsommar-film-review-1203247188/|archive-date=2019-06-19|title=‘Midsommar’ Film Review – Variety|date=2019-06-19|language=en|access-date=2020-08-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.themaineedge.com/buzz/movies/dark-waters-a-low-key-legal-drama|title=‘Dark Waters’ a low-key legal drama|first=Allen|last=Adams|website=www.themaineedge.com|access-date=2020-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191223043534/https://www.themaineedge.com/buzz/movies/dark-waters-a-low-key-legal-drama|archive-date=2019-12-23|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>

